message:
Hi, I work with the French indie studio Double Machine, and we’ve been working on a 2P co-op card-based guessing adventure game (Our Journey: The Silent Voice). I think you’ll enjoy playing it :)

The pitch: Your Body and Spirit have been separated. Communicate (only!) with cards and bring them back together. Embark on a unique 2 players co-op journey. If you enjoy games like It Takes Two and board games like Codenames, you’ll love this as well!

We've added a Twitch integration so you can also play with your chat.

I would like to send you 2 free Steam Keys, is it ok for you? :)

Hi, we’ve been working on a 2players co-op card-based guessing adventure game (it's called Our Journey: The Silent Voice). I genuinely think you’ll enjoy playing it :)


The pitch: Your Body and Spirit have been separated. Communicate (only!) with cards and bring them back together. If you enjoy games like It Takes Two and board games like Codenames, you’ll love this as well!

We've added a Twitch integration so you can also play with your chat.

I would like to send you 2 free Steam Keys, is it ok for you?  :)
